# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LOCAL overrides — NOT committed (git-ignored)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Shared, committed config lives in:
#   .env.development  -> loaded by `npm run dev`   (development mode)
#   .env.production   -> loaded by `npm run build` (production mode)
#
# Put any machine-specific override here to take precedence over
# the mode files above (e.g. point at a backend on your laptop):
#
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8081/api/v1/
# VITE_WAHA_URL=http://localhost:3000
# VITE_EVENT_SESSION_ID=replace-with-your-local-session-id
